This patch corrects defects in MIT contributed software: 2rtf and neos.

Manifest:
	contrib/mit/2rtf/2rtf.h (patch)
		don't redclare malloc and calloc on rs6k

	contrib/mit/neos/eosfx.c (patch)
		do not pre-declare macro functions that are later redeclared on solaris

	contrib/mit/neos/papers.c (patch)
		do not redeclare index (done for SYSV, though only tested on Soalris)

